                  <formatted-text>
                    <run fontsize='10'>Residual = median home value minus the average MedHouseVal for coastal vs inland (longitude split at −121°). Cells show AVG(residual) in ~0.2° bins. Warm colors = pricier than belt average; cool = cheaper. MedHouseVal is in hundreds of thousands of dollars ($100k).</run>
